                        Executive Order 13881,
July 15, 2019; and
                     </p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d1622e33" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(4)</ph>
                        Waiver of the domestic
content test of the Buy American statute for acquisitions of commercially
available off-the-shelf (COTS) items in accordance with 41 U.S.C.
1907, but see 25.201(b)(2)(ii).
                     </p>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </li>
